BT /F1 12 Tf 50 462 Td (   - Each router defines its own endpoints and controllers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 446 Td (   - Note: product.routes.ts is defined separately and should be imported) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 430 Td (     into this file to make /api/v1/products available.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 414 Td () Tj ET
