BT /F1 12 Tf 50 366 Td (     GET /:id, GET /brand/:brandId, GET /category/:categoryId, POST /,) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 350 Td (     PUT /:id, DELETE /:id.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 50 334 Td (   - Uses multer upload.fields\(\) for cover_image and images.) Tj ET
